snippet.title: The Settlers gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for The Settlers (aka serf city: life is feudal), Dos PC game produced by Blue Byte in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/the-settlers/1668/
Playing the first episode of the medieval saga. Building the village and get ready to fight for resources on the north..
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
The Settlers 2 - https://youtu.be/Qua2kb5GgQI
The Settlers 2 Gold Edition - https://youtu.be/fAwynE4BWC8
